---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { LorenzoComment } from '../components/LorenzoComment';
---

<Layout title="Agents Party | The Compendium">
  <main class="relative min-h-screen overflow-hidden text-ink-deep">
    <!-- Decorative Background Element -->
    <div
      class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full max-w-6xl aspect-square bg-gold-600/5 blur-[120px] rounded-full -z-10"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 relative">
      <!-- Navigation -->
      <nav class="flex justify-between items-center mb-16 bg-parchment-base border-[3px] border-ink-deep p-4 shadow-[4px_4px_0_var(--color-ink-deep)] rounded-sm">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 group">
          <div
            class="w-8 h-8 bg-crimson border-[2px] border-ink-deep shadow-[2px_2px_0_var(--color-ink-deep)] flex items-center justify-center group-hover:translate-y-[2px] group-hover:translate-x-[2px] group-hover:shadow-[0_0_0_var(--color-ink-deep)] transition-all"
          >
            <span class="text-white font-black text-lg leading-none font-mono">A</span>
          </div>
          <span
            class="font-black tracking-widest text-ink-deep uppercase text-sm group-hover:text-crimson transition-colors font-mono"
            >Agents Party</span
          >
        </a>
        <div class="hidden md:flex gap-8 text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-ink-deep font-mono items-center">
          <a href="/compendium" class="hover:text-crimson hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-transform"
            >Compendium</a
          >
          <a href="https://github.com/kelset/agent-party-planner" class="hover:text-crimson hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-transform flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.484 2 12.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0112 6.844c.85.004 1.705.115 2.504.337 1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.202 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.943.359.309.678.92.678 1.855 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.019 10.019 0 0022 12.017C22 6.484 17.522 2 12 2z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
            GitHub
          </a>
        </div>
      </nav>

      <!-- Content -->
      <article class="prose prose-invert max-w-none prose-h3:text-ink-deep prose-p:text-ink-faded prose-strong:text-ink-deep">
        <h1
          class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-parchment-light mb-8 tracking-widest uppercase drop-shadow-[4px_4px_0_var(--color-ink-deep)] font-mono"
        >
          The Compendium
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl text-ink-deep font-bold mb-12 leading-relaxed bg-parchment p-6 border-[3px] border-ink-deep shadow-[4px_4px_0_var(--color-ink-deep)] rounded-sm relative text-center">
          The <strong>Agents Party</strong> is an interactive web tool that
          lets you visually configure and export <em>Agent Orchestration</em> packages.
          Using a Dungeons &amp; Dragons theme, you can assemble a "Party" of specialized
          AI agents, customize their personalities, and download a ready-to-use orchestration
          setup tailored for platforms like Gemini or Claude. All entirely in your
          browser.
        </p>

        <h2
          class="text-2xl font-black text-parchment-light mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest border-b-[3px] border-ink-deep/50 pb-2 font-mono"
        >
          The Multi-Tier Architecture
        </h2>
        <LorenzoComment class="mb-12">
          The exported packages follow a strict 3-tier hierarchy that separates meta-planning<br class="hidden md:block"/> from actual coding. This ensures privacy, reduces clutter, and maintains clear roles.
        </LorenzoComment>

        <div class="space-y-8 mb-16">
          <section
            class="bg-parchment-base p-6 rounded-sm border-[3px] border-ink-deep shadow-[4px_4px_0_var(--color-ink-deep)] relative overflow-hidden"
          >
            <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 pointer-events-none" style={{ backgroundImage: 'linear-gradient(to right, #2c1e16 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(to bottom, #2c1e16 1px, transparent 1px)', backgroundSize: '16px 16px' }}></div>
            <h3
              class="text-xl font-black text-ink-deep mb-3 flex items-center gap-3 font-mono relative z-10"
            >
              <span class="text-gold-600 drop-shadow-[1px_1px_0_var(--color-ink-deep)]">I.</span> The Throne Room <span
                class="text-sm font-bold text-ink-faded tracking-widest uppercase"
                >(Meta-Level)</span
              >
            </h3>
            <p class="text-ink-faded font-bold relative z-10">
              The strategic layer where you interact with meta-agents to define
              the quest, set constraints, and adjust rules mid-flight. It runs
              in an isolated directory to keep your main codebase clean.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-ink-faded font-bold mt-4 space-y-2 relative z-10">
              <li>
                <strong class="text-crimson">The Game Creator:</strong> The architect
                and your primary brainstorming partner.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong class="text-crimson">The Master of Spies:</strong> The real-time
                analyst, critiquing orchestration inefficiencies.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong class="text-crimson">The Bard:</strong> The chronicler who
                translates technical achievements into an engaging narrative recap.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section
            class="bg-parchment-base p-6 rounded-sm border-[3px] border-ink-deep shadow-[4px_4px_0_var(--color-ink-deep)] relative overflow-hidden"
          >
            <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 pointer-events-none" style={{ backgroundImage: 'linear-gradient(to right, #2c1e16 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(to bottom, #2c1e16 1px, transparent 1px)', backgroundSize: '16px 16px' }}></div>
            <h3
              class="text-xl font-black text-ink-deep mb-3 flex items-center gap-3 font-mono relative z-10"
            >
              <span class="text-gold-600 drop-shadow-[1px_1px_0_var(--color-ink-deep)]">II.</span> The GM Session <span
                class="text-sm font-bold text-ink-faded tracking-widest uppercase"
                >(Coordinator)</span
              >
            </h3>
            <p class="text-ink-faded font-bold relative z-10">
              The Game Master (GM) runs inside the actual codebase. It acts as
              the project manager&mdash;reading journals, evaluating results,
              and spawning the correct Party Members to do the work. The GM
              coordinates but <em>never</em> writes code or runs tests itself.
            </p>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-black text-ink-deep mt-8 mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest font-mono relative z-10">Standard Quest Lifecycle</h4>
            
            <div class="relative pl-8 space-y-8 before:absolute before:inset-y-0 before:left-[11px] before:w-[3px] before:bg-ink-deep mt-6 pb-4 relative z-10 font-bold">
              <!-- Phase 1 -->
              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute -left-[39px] -top-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-sm bg-parchment border-[3px] border-ink-deep shadow-[2px_2px_0_var(--color-ink-deep)] flex items-center justify-center">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-sm bg-emerald-500"></span>
                </div>
                <h5 class="text-ink-deep font-black mb-2 tracking-widest uppercase text-sm font-mono">Phase 1: Recon</h5>
                <div class="bg-parchment p-4 rounded-sm border-[3px] border-ink-deep flex flex-col gap-3 text-sm shadow-[2px_2px_0_var(--color-ink-deep)]">
                  <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="text-xl drop-shadow-sm">🏹</span>
                    <div class="text-ink-faded"><strong class="text-emerald-600 font-black tracking-wide">Ranger</strong> gathers baseline measurements and maps the environment.</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="text-xl drop-shadow-sm">🧙‍♂️</span>
                    <div class="text-ink-faded"><strong class="text-purple-600 font-black tracking-wide">Wizard</strong> analyzes the data and writes a structured attack plan.</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- Phase 2 -->
              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute -left-[39px] -top-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-sm bg-parchment border-[3px] border-ink-deep shadow-[2px_2px_0_var(--color-ink-deep)] flex items-center justify-center">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-sm bg-crimson"></span>
                </div>
                <h5 class="text-ink-deep font-black mb-2 tracking-widest uppercase text-sm font-mono">Phase 2: Execution <span class="text-ink-faded text-xs normal-case">(Iterative Loop)</span></h5>
                <div class="bg-parchment p-4 rounded-sm border-[3px] border-ink-deep flex flex-col gap-3 text-sm shadow-[2px_2px_0_var(--color-ink-deep)]">
                  <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="text-xl drop-shadow-sm">⚔️</span>
                    <div class="text-ink-faded"><strong class="text-crimson font-black tracking-wide">Warrior</strong> implements the specific changes according to the plan.</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-2 pl-4 text-ink-light">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 stroke-[3px]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="miter" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"></path></svg>
                    <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-black">Loop until approved</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="text-xl drop-shadow-sm">🧛‍♂️</span>
                    <div class="text-ink-faded"><strong class="text-purple-800 font-black tracking-wide">Warlock</strong> scrutinizes the code. Blocks bad changes or approves.</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="mt-2 pt-3 border-t-[3px] border-ink-deep/20 flex flex-col gap-3">
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                      <span class="text-xl drop-shadow-sm">🧙‍♂️</span>
                      <div class="text-ink-faded"><strong class="text-purple-600 font-black tracking-wide">Wizard</strong> &amp; <strong class="text-emerald-600 font-black tracking-wide">Ranger</strong> verify the final outcome matches the plan and metrics.</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-3 opacity-80">
                      <span class="text-xl drop-shadow-sm">🧑‍⚕️</span>
                      <div class="text-ink-faded"><em>If blockers hit:</em> <strong class="text-cyan-700 font-black tracking-wide">Healer</strong> diagnoses and recovers the environment.</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- Phase 3 -->
              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute -left-[39px] -top-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-sm bg-parchment border-[3px] border-ink-deep shadow-[2px_2px_0_var(--color-ink-deep)] flex items-center justify-center">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-sm bg-gold-400"></span>
                </div>
                <h5 class="text-ink-deep font-black mb-2 tracking-widest uppercase text-sm font-mono">Phase 3: Document & Report</h5>
                <div class="bg-parchment p-4 rounded-sm border-[3px] border-ink-deep flex items-start gap-3 text-sm shadow-[2px_2px_0_var(--color-ink-deep)]">
                  <span class="text-xl drop-shadow-sm">📜</span>
                  <div class="text-ink-faded">The GM records final measurements, writes the summary log, and reports back to the Throne Room.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section
            class="bg-parchment-base p-6 rounded-sm border-[3px] border-ink-deep shadow-[4px_4px_0_var(--color-ink-deep)] relative overflow-hidden"
          >
            <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 pointer-events-none" style={{ backgroundImage: 'linear-gradient(to right, #2c1e16 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(to bottom, #2c1e16 1px, transparent 1px)', backgroundSize: '16px 16px' }}></div>
            <h3
              class="text-xl font-black text-ink-deep mb-3 flex items-center gap-3 font-mono relative z-10"
            >
              <span class="text-gold-600 drop-shadow-[1px_1px_0_var(--color-ink-deep)]">III.</span> The Party <span
                class="text-sm font-bold text-ink-faded tracking-widest uppercase"
                >(Sub-Agents)</span
              >
            </h3>
            <p class="text-ink-faded font-bold mb-4 relative z-10">
              The specialized workers executing the tasks. The magic lies in
              their <strong>constructive tension</strong>: they are not yes-men,
              but experts who push back on bad plans and scrutinize each other's
              work.
            </p>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm relative z-10 font-bold">
              <div
                class="bg-parchment p-4 rounded-sm border-[3px] border-ink-deep shadow-[2px_2px_0_var(--color-ink-deep)]"
              >
                <strong class="text-emerald-600 block mb-1 font-black tracking-widest uppercase font-mono"
                  >🏹 Ranger (Telemetry)</strong
                >
                <span class="text-ink-faded"
                  >Data gatherer. No ego, just numbers.</span
                >
              </div>
              <div
                class="bg-parchment p-4 rounded-sm border-[3px] border-ink-deep shadow-[2px_2px_0_var(--color-ink-deep)]"
              >
                <strong class="text-purple-600 block mb-1 font-black tracking-widest uppercase font-mono"
                  >🧙‍♂️ Wizard (Strategist)</strong
                >
                <span class="text-ink-faded"
                  >Creates ambitious attack plans.</span
                >
              </div>
              <div
                class="bg-parchment p-4 rounded-sm border-[3px] border-ink-deep shadow-[2px_2px_0_var(--color-ink-deep)]"
              >
                <strong class="text-crimson block mb-1 font-black tracking-widest uppercase font-mono"
                  >⚔️ Warrior (Implementation)</strong
                >
                <span class="text-ink-faded"
                  >Pragmatic shipper. Writes the code.</span
                >
              </div>
              <div
                class="bg-parchment p-4 rounded-sm border-[3px] border-ink-deep shadow-[2px_2px_0_var(--color-ink-deep)]"
              >
                <strong class="text-purple-800 block mb-1 font-black tracking-widest uppercase font-mono"
                  >🧛‍♂️ Warlock (Code Review)</strong
                >
                <span class="text-ink-faded"
                  >Adversarial critic. Blocks bad code.</span
                >
              </div>
              <div
                class="bg-parchment p-4 rounded-sm border-[3px] border-ink-deep shadow-[2px_2px_0_var(--color-ink-deep)] md:col-span-2"
              >
                <strong class="text-cyan-700 block mb-1 font-black tracking-widest uppercase font-mono"
                  >🧑‍⚕️ Healer (Diagnostics)</strong
                >
                <span class="text-ink-faded"
                  >Systematic fixer and environment recovery.</span
                >
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </article>

      <div class="mt-16 text-center">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="inline-block px-10 py-4 bg-crimson hover:bg-crimson-hover text-white font-black rounded-sm shadow-[4px_4px_0_var(--color-ink-deep)] transition-all uppercase tracking-widest text-sm border-[3px] border-ink-deep active:translate-y-[4px] active:translate-x-[4px] active:shadow-[0_0_0_var(--color-ink-deep)] font-mono"
        >
          Assemble Your Party
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer
      class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 mt-8 border-t-[3px] border-ink-deep/30 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6 text-ink-deep text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono"
    >
      <span>© 2026 Agents Party</span>
      <div class="flex gap-8 text-center md:text-left">
        <span>Made with agentic nerdism by <a href="https://kelset.dev" class="hover:text-crimson hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-transform">kelset</a></span>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/kelset/agent-party-planner"
          class="hover:text-crimson hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-transform">GitHub</a
        >
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>
</Layout>
